Inspired by the Tigo Integration work of MartinStoffel.

This fork (https://github.com/TerryFrench/tigosolar-online) adds support for
the Tigo v4 cloud API (mapi.tigoenergy.com) with v3 fallback, premium-account
handling, token lifecycle management, incremental fetching, resilient backoff
that respects server throttling, Home Assistant Energy Dashboard compatibility,
inverter/string device modelling, and shareable diagnostics/debug logging.

